abstract: Katie Ledecky wins 800-meter freestyle at Arena Pro Swim Series in Texas.
lead_paragraph: Ledecky wrapped up the Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Austin, Tex., by dominating the 800-meter freestyle for her fourth gold medal of the event.
